description: KFYP tracks the CSI CICC Select 100 Index, which takes a smart-beta1 approach to systematically invest in companies listed in Mainland China. The strategy is based on China International Capital Corporation (CICC)’s latest research on China’s capital markets. This quantitative approach reflects CICC’s top down and bottom up research process, seeking to deliver the 100 leading companies in Mainland China.
name: KraneShares CICC China Leaders 100 Index ETF*
